enhanced_by.reason: The nonUniqueIndexedCollection method initializes an IndexedCollection object, similar to the constructor.
The add method handles the addition of elements to the collection, similar to how nonUniqueIndexedCollection initializes and manages the collection.
The reindex method re-indexes the entire collection, which can be used to verify the state of the collection after initialization by nonUniqueIndexedCollection.
